<div class ="paragraph">
<h2> Steve Longo (Brother of the groom) – Best Man </h2>
<p> Steve is a full-service one-stop-shop of a big brother.  He is a man of many talents. </p>


<h3> He can: </h3>

<ul>
<li> Replace your light bulbs </li>
<li> Fix your television, garbage disposal, icemaker, furnace, bathroom sink </li>
<li> Pick you up from the airport on a minute’s notice </li>
<li> Walk your dog </li>
<li> Taste-test your cooking </li>
<li> Assess and advise on your financial portfolio </li>
<li> Solve your worst logistical problems </li>
