<li> Feverishly root for your college football team, your fantasy team, or any team you ask him to. </li>
<li> Give awesome “Steve lectures” (“Steve, why are New York subways so confusing?  How did the Gregorian and Julian calendars influence international conflict?  Why did the Borg name Locutus?")  </li>
