<div class ="paragraph">
<h2> Erin Basch (Sister-in-law of the groom)  </h2>
<p> Erin joined the Longo extended family in 2013 when she married Mo.  She is incredibly creative.  She appreciates all sorts of music – everything from classical music to Nas and Eazy-E.  She knows exactly how to turn that frown upside-down.  She is a LIL (Longo-in-Law) and is prepared to induct Riley into this exclusive club.  She is an avid Browns fan and we hope she enjoys her time in Pittsburgh.
</p>
<p> We are so grateful that she is part of our family, and we look forward to picking her brain for music suggestions! </p>
