<h2> Conor Ryan (Future brother-in-law of the bride) </h2>
<p> Conor will be marrying Andrea in October 2015, at which time he will join Tom in becoming a “Smythe” (ask any of the extended Graham family what this means). Like Riley, Andrea, Erin, and Mo, Conor also attended the University of Dayton where he participated in band with Erin and Mo.  Conor works for PNC, which we presume is only temporary until one of his many ideas catches fire.  Are you interested in having a robot make your sandwich?  If so, please talk to Conor about an investment opportunity.
</p>
<p>Conor is a genuine guy and we are thrilled to have him in our wedding and in our family!</p>
